The paper discusses the development of technical systems that implement the idea of Strong Intelligence, which is a core topic in the field of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The focus of the paper is on the perception of the external world, which is a key area of research in neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the creation of intelligent systems, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY).
